title: The Jennie Garth Project S01E01-03 WS DSR x264 NY2
description:
Recently single actress and mom of three Jennie Garth takes on a major renovation when she guts and remodels a 1970s ranch house in Hollywood Hills and turns it into her dream home.
Episode 1- A bold design choice to improve curb appeal is made in the premiere of this series, which folllows single mom of three Jennie Garth as she takes on a major renovation, gutting and remodeling a 1970s ranch house in Hollywood Hills.
Episode 2-The living room is transformed, but first Jennie must tackle a costly repair and reevaluate her design plan.
Episode 3- Jennie's family weigh in on her plan for a guest suite with its own private garden.
